		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Even if you aren't doing "NTSC emulation", it might be best to understand the emphasis in the component (YUV) domain, and then use the same YUV-to-RGB transformation that you use for your emulator's current NTSC palette generator.

		

		</td>
